{"tid":435641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[一做樓奴 深似海]單幢唐樓維修索每戶250萬！","createTime":"2017-10-14T12:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T02:29:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2d398d5d2513f64fe1f3667f7ab2281dd3d7d0","tid":435641,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:50:35.000Z","msg":"深水埗大南街單幢式唐樓業主法團主席伍女士表示，其法團於2009年參加樓宇更新大行動，首次招標時選擇了報價3萬至4萬港元的工程顧問，其價錢屬於中等水平，結果工程承建商招標報價後每戶卻需攤分210萬港元，且此價不包括消防改善工程。法團認為工程費太貴，遂重新招標，但第二次招標報價反<span style=\"color: red;\">升至每戶需攤分250萬港元。</span><br />\n<br />\n伍續指，法團於是在第三次招標中選擇最貴的工程顧問，索價18萬港元，對方表明若工程報價不低於房協獨立估價便不收費，結果其後的工程承建商招標報價降至190萬港元，當中包括消防改善工程，並低於房協提供的200萬港元獨立估價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171014/bkn-20171014120908498-1014_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171014%2Fbkn-20171014120908498-1014_00822_001.html&d=qXMKaK5z5ZTd9Qcqkt%2FpdP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=34d54a91\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171014/bkn-20171014120908498-1014_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4594697da0e55361b108a13d7616806dbb7627e7","tid":435641,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e88edeffb76c22924910c93c68f5cccab7406f3","tid":435641,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9a638af6d65a4f43cb8751a2e951923ac1b1fc7e","tid":435641,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1455d5262deefc0c2ff1d139d2a235ff4c6e5ceb","tid":435641,"uid":50